gw.api.desktop

Class DesktopAwaitingAssignmentFilterSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • gw.api.filters.FilterSetBase
      • gw.api.activity.ActivityFilterSetBase
        • gw.api.desktop.DesktopAwaitingAssignmentFilterSet

  • public class DesktopAwaitingAssignmentFilterSet
extends ActivityFilterSetBase
    Filters used on the desktop "awaiting assignment" page. These filters assume the base query does not do any filtering at all.

    Note: This FilterSet used to live in the file DesktopAwaitingAssignmentAction.java.
